    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> chopped hake</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>marinated hake</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>gram flour</strong> to a separate bowl with your <strong>ground cumin </strong>and most of your <strong>cayenne</strong> <strong>pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>spiced</strong> <strong>gram flour</strong></p>",
